#

Truffle Mushroom Risotto with Asparagus Tips and Parmesan Crisp

$15
620 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

ItalianGourmetComfort Food

Description

A luxurious risotto infused with truffle oil, featuring wild mushrooms and fresh asparagus, topped with a crisp Parmesan wafer.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • Fresh truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Wild mushrooms (e.g., shiitake, oyster): 1 cup, sliced
  • Asparagus tips: 1 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Shallots: 1, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
